Company Summary

          Virtu Financial Inc is a leading technology-enabled market maker and liquidity provider to the global financial markets. It maintains a technology platform which provides quotations to buyers and sellers in equities, global currencies, fixed income, global commodities (including energy and metals), options, and other securities. The system provides quotations for more than 12,000 securities on more than 230 unique exchanges, markets, and liquidity pools around the world. The group generates revenue by buying and selling large volumes of securities and other financial instruments and earning small bid/ask spreads. In addition, it also earns revenues from interest and dividend income as well as through the sale of licensed technology and related services.
        
